ENTRY       EC 1.3.99.30                Enzyme
NAME        phytoene desaturase (3,4-didehydrolycopene-forming);
            5-step phytoene desaturase;
            five-step phytoene desaturase;
            phytoene desaturase (ambiguous);
            Al-1
CLASS       Oxidoreductases;
            Acting on the CH-CH group of donors;
            With other acceptors
SYSNAME     15-cis-phytoene:acceptor oxidoreductase (3,4-didehydrolycopene-forming)
REACTION    15-cis-phytoene + 5 acceptor = all-trans-3,4-didehydrolycopene + 5 reduced acceptor (overall reaction) [RN:R09703];
            (1a) 15-cis-phytoene + acceptor = all-trans-phytofluene + reduced acceptor [RN:R09692];
            (1b) all-trans-phytofluene + acceptor = all-trans-zeta-carotene + reduced acceptor [RN:R04787];
            (1c) all-trans-zeta-carotene + acceptor = all-trans-neurosporene + reduced acceptor [RN:R04798];
            (1d) all-trans-neurosporene + acceptor = all-trans-lycopene + reduced acceptor [RN:R04800];
            (1e) all-trans-lycopene + acceptor = all-trans-3,4-didehydrolycopene + reduced acceptor [RN:R07518]
ALL_REAC    R04787 R04798 R04800 R07518 R09692 R09703
SUBSTRATE   15-cis-phytoene [CPD:C05421];
            acceptor [CPD:C00028];
            all-trans-phytofluene [CPD:C05414];
            all-trans-zeta-carotene [CPD:C05430];
            all-trans-neurosporene [CPD:C05431];
            all-trans-lycopene [CPD:C05432]
PRODUCT     all-trans-3,4-didehydrolycopene [CPD:C15867];
            reduced acceptor [CPD:C00030];
            all-trans-phytofluene [CPD:C05414];
            all-trans-zeta-carotene [CPD:C05430];
            all-trans-neurosporene [CPD:C05431];
            all-trans-lycopene [CPD:C05432]
COMMENT     This enzyme is involved in carotenoid biosynthesis and catalyses up to five desaturation steps (cf. EC 1.3.99.28 [phytoene desaturase (neurosporene-forming)], EC 1.3.99.29 [phytoene desaturase (zeta-carotene-forming)] and EC 1.3.99.31 [phytoene desaturase (lycopene-forming)]).
